            "value": "<p>Prized by naari geniekin who prefer to fight with their fists, <em>major scalding gauntlets</em> are a pair of <em>+2 greater striking flaming spiked gauntlets</em>. The intricate golden gauntlets are engraved with Pyric writing praising the glories of the Dominion of Flame and embellished with shimmering black and red gemstones. A creature you grab or restrain while wearing the gauntlets must succeed at a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:32] save or take [[/r 3d6[persistent,fire]]] damage and be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1} from the pain; it's temporarily immune to being sickened by <em>scalding gauntlets</em> for 1 hour.</p>"
